data.description: Great starter brick home in Lancaster. This cutie was recently remodeled and it's now ready for its new owner! Home now offers new laminate floors, new kitchen appliances, new interior paint, among other upgrades and updates.  It features a split bedrooms arrangement, 1 bath. Sits on a large lot! ideal for the growing family and gatherings. Ample kitchen with exterior door to the huge back yard. The window and door casing provide a nice, cozy, warmth feel in the living area. No carpet! Convenient laminate floors throughout and ceramic tile in the bathroom. Come check it out!
